Text.string: Hey turd farmers! Check this out!
Man, that thing looks dangerous! So, what, like, it gives you super powers or something? Kinda want to lick it...
You're right, Ava! I... I have to be strong for the people who look up to me!
I've never seen such power.
If we don't stop Troy soon, he's gonna tear Pandora apart.
You must cut off Troy's Eridium supply, Vault Hunter. Pandora's fate is in your hands. No pressure.
Yo, fam! Kill the Vault Hunters for me, would ya please? We're sorta busy at the moment.

Stop coddling them, Tyreen! Listen, you filthy, demented mouth breathers! I'm charging an entire goddamn moon, so WHY THE HELL ARE THE VAULT THIEVES STILL ALIVE?! Kill them now, or I'll RIP YOU APART AND PISS ON YOUR ASHES!
Ground assaults are my specialty.
Heh. With pleasure.
I will take them apart.
I've been waitin' for this.
Vault Hunter, you did it! Troy stopped charging Elpis.
Yeah! Go team!
Ain't that somethin'.
Mmmm, that was some GOOD boom! [sighs]
How... Tannis, the Vault Hunter cut off his Eridium supply. Where's Troy getting that kind of power?
I have a theory, but you aren't going to like it, Lilith.
Death wishes are also my specialty.
Ooh, ooh! Also me.
A Death wish, you say? I wish for nothing else.
Zane “Deathwish” Flynt, at your service!
Tyreen. He's using Tyreen. He's leeching his own sister to keep charging Elpis! Vault Hunter—you have to take out Troy. It's the only way!
You don't get it, do you, Vault Thief? We're family—and no sacrifice is too great for your family!
I'll cover you, Vault Hunter, you got this. For Maya.
Troy! It hurts!
Keep going! Our viewership's through the roof!
Troy, I can't handle this much longer!
Don't you DARE quit on me now!
Stop! You're gonna kill me!
RGAGHHHHH!
Not much longer, Tyreen. Hold on!
Ty! I need more power. Stop fighting me!
Keep it together, Ty! We're so close! I can feel it!
Tyreen, come on! Give me all you've got!
Rgh—hang in there, Ty! Be stronger!
We're almost there. Don't quit on me, Ty!
This is my moment. This is OUR moment!
We've got this, Ty! We're gonna open the Great Vault!
Finally, Ty! We're so close!
It's on. Time to ice those Calypsos and save Pandora. Then we're gonna party, BALEX-style.
Tyreen... no!||—Cut the feed now! Turn off the goddamn cameras!
You... YOU did this!
It's over. That's what matters.
Well, time to be a hero! Whenever I imagined saving the world, it was always by curing a bio-plague I'd accidentally unleashed.

Who? How did you get this—no, you know what? It doesn't matter. This is Typhon DeLeon. Listen up—you see that crazy beam of light shooting through the sky? Pretty cool, right? Well, that means the Great Vault is opening. And if it does, say goodbye to Pandora! So get your keister to Nekrotafeyo, NOW!
Ty... we were so close...
A-Are they dead?
I'm on my way!
Maya...
Those powers never truly belonged to Troy. And now it seems they have found their rightful owner.
Maya had a plan all along. Heh. Those suit you, Ava.
But... what about you?
Yeah.||Wow, look.
Beautiful. Terrifying, but beautiful nonetheless.
Well? Where do you wanna go?
What the hell?
You did it, Troy.
Now let's finish this together.
Hell yeah, that'll do it.
Do you feel that? There's a god waking up beneath our feet, and we just took off its chains.
Soon the Destroyer will be free. And once I leech it—well, I'll be the only star left in the sky.
Buh-bye now!
Heh.
And we are live! Heh, well, not them. They're SUPER dead.
Aww, you thought you were gonna win? Maybe next time, superfans... or not, that's just something people say. Game over, bitches!
What's happening?
The Great Vault is opening...
Nothing's gonna stop us now.
Pandora. Pandora is the Great Vault.
Hello? Hello?! Is anyone there? What have you done? The universe is doomed!
Whose ECHO is that?
Vault Hunter, check it out.
This is Moze, copy.
This is Amara, copy.
This is FL4K, copy.
Zane here. Over.
Impossible. He's been missing for decades ever since he vowed to find the legendary planet of...
Nekrotafeyo. Maya used to tell me stories about it.
What is going on?
Pandora's not a planet. It's the Great Vault.
And Tyreen intends to leech the planet-sized monster within.
RAAGAAGHAHGHH!
The Destroyer. It's still alive. That's what Tyreen meant when she told me she'd finish what I started.
Back to the ship, everyone. We have to find Nekrotafeyo.
And meet the Vault Hunter who started it all.
Here, Ava. You take it.
That actually worked!
You catch on quick. Good save.
Tannis' device is safe? Good job, killer. Come up to Sanctuary. It's time to plan the attack.
Okay. Tannis' Eridium amplifier is in place and Vaughn's forces on the ground are at the ready. We're not gonna get a better chance to move on the Calypsos.
See, I WAS planning to leech enough Vault monsters to charge it myself, but... then you handed us your stupid Siren friend, and now Troy can just use Eridium!
Maya. Avenged.
That was for Maya.
Maya has been avenged.
That was for Maya, ya langer!
Lilith, we must stop Troy from opening the Great Vault, but as long as he is infusing himself with Eridium he will be nearly invincible.
We got this! Keep goin', Vault Hunter. Do what you do, you freakin' maestro of mayhem or whatever!
Hahahahaha! Been waitin' for this, Vault Thief!
Ohohhohoho! We're gonna be gods, bitches! Ha-HA!
Incoming transmission from the—
The Calypsos. Got it. This should be interesting.
Ay, pero, how did you, like, phaselock the entire moon? Wow.
Ava, you good to back up the Vault Hunter?
You were right. We've gotta run towards the fire. Let's go, everyone.

Heya, sugar. Off to shut those Calypso twerps up for good, are you? Well, I feel better knowing the fate of the world rests in your... capable hands. Before you leave, you might wanna give my slots one last go—I've got a feeling it's your lucky day.
Whoa! This bronette is charging! Go go go go go! Siren liiiiife!
Over here, killer.
Well, well, well. I'd wish you good luck, but it doesn't seem like you need any more.

Ah, Vault Hunter! So, we've reached the proverbial end of the road, it seems. I have the utmost faith in your ability to throw your enemies screaming into the void. You typically do—but, just to make sure, Wainwright and I want you to have this!
It has come to this. / The battle to end a war. / Crush them, Vault Hunter.
I am ready... I hope.
Oh, my...
I feel... powerful!
Oh my...
The moon... that enough of a fire for you, Ava?
Yo, Vault Hunter! Tina gave me these. You do the honors.
What's up, door? You got NOTHIN'! Thanks, Tina!
He said Typhon DeLeon...
I got you, Ava! You my flaaava!
We gotta cut off Troy's Eridium supply. There's no way he can keep phaselocking the moon without Eridium. This way!
Yo, Vault Hunter—entrance is up ahead. I'll meet you there!
Vault Hunter! Troy's Eridium supply is flowing through those statues. Let's see if we can cut him off from the source!
Looks like we can open those hatches. The switches up there should do it.
All right, chuck a grenade down there.
Nice throw!
Good one!
A weak spot! Nice. Shoot it, Vault Hunter!
Now stop Troy. Put an end to this.
Take a look out the window. Troy's about to blow your spine out your ass.
I got your back, Vault Hunter. Kill that maniac. For Maya.
Agh—Troy, you're taking too much! Gahhhhghgh!
Uhh, it's the freaking MOON, you idiots! The key to the Great Vault has been in front of your dumb faces the whole time.
There IS still a Vault here. Vault Hunter, you should go and see what is inside. I imagine we will need every advantage we can get.
God power, bitches!

This isn't the Great Vault itself. The Calypsos were in possession of the Pandoran key for quite a while. They could have looted this Vault ages ago, but they didn't. Perhaps what is inside is not power, but knowledge. Knowledge that they already had.

Incredible. That device appears to be capable of translating Eridian language! That's something that has eluded even the top researchers in the field for decades! And yes, I do mean me. This will need further study. Return to me, Vault Hunter.
Once I charge Elpis, the Great Vault will open...
I'll leech the monster inside, and—heh, we become Gods!
She's flying!
Very good. When you return to Sanctuary, please go to my lab first. I suspect that analyzer might be a missing piece in a puzzle I have been trying to solve.
(waking up, crawling efforts)
We'd invite you to our place for the grand opening, but, uh... ehh, it's kind of a family thing.
See you at the end of the world!
I'm doomed! Unless... is it too late to join the COV?
(jolt react)
(jolt react)
(jolt react)
(bracing effort)
(bracing effort)
Ride, bro, ride!
(bracing effort)
(bracing reaction)
Then we cut off his supply. Vault Hunter, once Tannis takes out those turrets, you lead a ground assault.
And whoever has a death wish can take on Tyreen and Troy!
Yeah? You sure?
(bracing reaction)
(bracing reaction)
Vault Hunter. Get geared up and say your goodbyes. This is it.
Talk to me before you head down there, killer.
I always thought the Calypsos becoming gods was simply rhetoric, but if Tyreen leeches the monster in the Great Vault... well, what is God but the most powerful being in the universe?
Let's take those Calypsos down!
I wasn't sure what to do after Maya... well, you know. But you just kept moving. You never let anything stop you, Vault Hunter. So let's take 'em down together. For Maya.
(bracing reaction)
(bracing reaction)
I'd say I hate to watch you go, Vault Hunter, but me and you both know that ain't true. Protect that fine ass when you're down there. I'll be rooting for ya!

Vault Hunter! When you save the world, no one's gonna say ol' Marcus didn't do his part. So, just this one time, here's some... ammo... on the house.||Don't tell anyone about this. And don't die down there. You're my favorite customer.

Look, I'm basically an expert on saving the world, so here's a little advice for my favorite recruit. When you're staring down the ugly maw of death, just remember that there are plenty more Vault Hunters where you came from, so the Crimson Raiders will be just fine!||—That was my best pep talk yet!
All set, killer?
Oh yeah. Iron Bear's jonesin' for a fight.
Always ready. Time for the big finale.
I will answer Death's call, wherever she leads me.
I was born ready. And handsome. Full head of hair.
It's time to beat some COV ass and take down the Calypsos. Head to Roland's Rest. Vaughn and Tannis will be ready for you.
Vault Hunter! It is time! Once you take down those turrets, we'll storm the stronghold together!
Bandit liiiiife!
Vault Hunter, I'll meet you up ahead. If I'm to moonlight as a hero, I should use the vernacular, yes? It is... “go time”!
Drive, Vault Hunter.
I'm waiting, Vault Hunter.
Pick me up, Vault Hunter.
Now drive, Vault Hunter. Drive like you're heading for a cliff with a loved one! But to my position.
You're here! Clear the area, Vault Hunter. I'll need to focus while I whisper sweet electrical nothings to those turrets.
(bracing reaction)
(land react)
Executing phaseshift. Let the controlled chaos commence!
One turret taken over. Onward to the next one!
The second turret is mine! And it apologized for shooting at you earlier.
I've taken over all of the turrets and promised them amnesty. Please welcome the newest members of the Crimson Raiders.
Phaseshift complete. With heroic flair, I might add!
Crimson Raider for liiiiife!
Hell yeah! Storm the gates! Blood feuuuuuuuud! I'm tryin' to mix up how I say that every time.
Get in there, killer. You have to stop Troy before he charges Elpis.
For Rhys-ball! And, you know, the-the-the-the-the Crimson Raiders, too! Go team!
Jakobs rides with you as well, Vault Hunter. Let's show them zealots the might of the Crimson Raiders!
Let's do this shiz! B-Team, Operation Wild Ride is a go-go, go-go, go-go-GO!
Aight, my lovely ambassadors of death. To the gates post-haste! Oh, because this is a suicide mission, Mordy, I CUT ALL YOUR BRAKES!
Very funny, Tina—DIOS MIO, SHE ACTUALLY DID IT!
Tina! Not cool!
Gahahahaha! Woooooo! Don't stop till the Calypsos DROP!
Those cultists aren't messin' around!
Clear the area, Vault Hunter. I can't concentrate amidst these screaming masses.
I can't focus with this “riffed raff” hollering and threatening me.
Vault Hunter, could you kindly destroy all the COV in the area?
I cannot phaseshift under these conditions.
Easy, bird man! Fly low, and fly faaast!
We got this, ya'll! Bahahahaha!
(land react)
(land react)
Take 'em down, Vault Hunter.
Get it together, Claptrap.
Full moon party! Woohoo! I can feel that god-fire pumpin' through my veins! I'm burnin' brighter than a supernova!
Attention Eridium-tier followers: put on your limited edition starglasses so you can gaze upon us without going blind! Gods, bitches! It's happening!
You worthless nothings. Kill the Vault Thieves. Now!
Listen to my brother, lovelies. The Great Vault beckons! Our moment of transcendence is at hand! Keep the heretics at bay while we prepare for our divine transformation!
Drown the Vault Thieves in your own blood if you have to. I don't care, just get it done!
